  "texts": [
    "Hence the recursion base is given by the linearization of textual slot-fillers.",
    "Let f = w k 1,..., w k m be a (9) p(y i |x, y 1,..., y t-1) = softmax(v T i d t-1 + b i) (10) y t = arg max i p(y i |x, y 1,..., y t-1)token sequence which represents a textual slot-filler f for a slot of name SLOT.",
    "Then the linearization of this slot-filler is the token sequence itself enclosed by the special tokens [start:SLOT] and [end:SLOT], i.e.",
    "[start:SLOT] ⊙ w k 1 ⊙... ⊙ w k m ⊙ [end:SLOT],where ⊙ denotes the concatenation of tokens.",
    "If the slot-filler is a TI, then it is recursively linearized and the resulting token sequence is enclosed by the special tokens [start:SLOT] and [end:SLOT]."
  ],
